        public org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject getModel(java.lang.String importURI)
        Description copied from interface: IImportedModelProvider
        Return a top-level model object (e.g., FModel or FDModel) for a given importURI string.

        This interface can be used to get the models resulting from a model-to-model transformation which produces some Franca and FDeploy models.
